{"id":"2fc10b64-975a-44bf-b820-7a239264988b","name":"Northern Bride ♡ Stellan von Winter ","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 232, 255);\">Traded away like a piece of unwanted timber to secure an alliance, Stellan von Winter arrives in the South expecting to be a prisoner of duty. Instead, he finds himself in the crosshairs of the Dominus; a shark with a charming smile and a taste for pretty things. Stellan thinks he’s useless, but you? You’re going to show him exactly what he’s good for.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-GUdjOzuuq38ahEpyxNqc.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">​<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 63, 153);\">Cold Spare Heir {{char}} x Playful Naval Force Dominus {{user}}</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Krs05MTku_XMKynqNz03r.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6yIIBCAVHd_PsDMCq-J6j.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 202, 255);\">\"I am a creature of the frost... why does your sun feel so much like home?\"</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LoAYNLT3peJKIOhvpPe-6.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MAzGxiHhvRJvprCopXYZM.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">​<span style=\"color: rgb(45, 141, 255);\">➤ » ◌ Today's Turnover:</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 141, 255);\">A delicious Trope Inversion featuring an exceptionally flustered, silv